---
<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-slate-950 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative background elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-yellow-400/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-900/10 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/3"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-yellow-400 transform rotate-3 rounded-2xl"></div>
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" 
          alt="Our Team" 
          class="relative rounded-2xl shadow-2xl transform -rotate-3 transition-transform hover:rotate-0 duration-500"
        />
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-yellow-400 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-2">About Us</h2>
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-montserrat">
          Beyond celebration, we deliver <br/><span class="italic text-yellow-200">peace of mind</span>.
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Fjord & Flavors Events is built on the promise of "Nordic Precision. Authentic Flavors." 
          We combine the vibrant culinary traditions of Spain and Norway with the structure, reliability, and safety of professional event logistics.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-slate-900 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Our Commitment</h4>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <div class="flex items-center text-gray-400">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Professional planning
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center text-gray-400">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Reliable logistics
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center text-gray-400">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Clear communication
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center text-gray-400">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Full compliance
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center text-gray-400">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                High-quality execution
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center text-gray-400">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Zero improvisation
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
            <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Who we work with:</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Private clients (Christenings, Weddings) • Corporate teams • International clients in Norway</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
